{
  "stem": "23942.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He-- he was doing-- he was working with children who survived and he was bringing them here, bringing them there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He was-- he was involved with Jewish children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he came and picked me up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He was told-- I was told that he's taking me to-- to [INAUDIBLE], to Zabrze.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I didn't even remember for years where this was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was a little vill-- suburb near Katowice, not far from Katowice, in the suburbs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Zabrze, a small, little, like a sort of village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You know, it looks like a village, but, you know, small houses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And this Zabrze, there was a-- a home for children.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was a very well run-- very, very well run.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I have to say that that home was the first time I realized after the war that I belonged there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I felt like I really belonged there, that I-- this is where I belong temporarily.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "In other words, that I must never run away from there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "In other words, that there's nothing better waiting for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In other words, he told me on the plane-- on the train, he says, you mustn't run away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "He already knew my-- what I went through, so he realized I was no ordinary child, that I had went through tremendous things.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he talked to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And he made me feel so good that I never forgot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He-- he said to me, you must stay, and they're going to treat you wonderful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "He got through to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He got through to me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "The way he spoke to me, I realized that this man was special.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "He was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, my friend remembers and I can't remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- sometimes I have-- I wrote it down, but I can't remember right now.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
